  <text>
    <body>
      <p>
        <s><kinesic><desc>Hmm</desc></kinesic>, why did <name type="person">Nick</name> invite me without <name type="person">Tom</name>?</s>
        <s>Did they have a fight?</s>
        <s>To be honest, it will probably do me good to be away from him for a while.</s>
        <s>My life with him can be such a burden sometimes.</s>
        <s>If it weren't for our daughter and his money...</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>Is <name type="person">Nick</name> coming?</s>
        <s>Good.</s>
        <s>Smile, <name type="person">Daisy</name>.</s>
        <s>Smile!</s>
        <s>He's your cousin.</s>
        <s>He has no fault.</s>
        <s>He likes you, you like him.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>His house is not that big... that's not really all he can afford, is it?</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s><kinesic><desc>Hmm</desc></kinesic>?</s>
        <s>What's funny though?</s>
        <s>It's just a living room.</s>
        <s>Is he okay?</s>
        <s>Someone's knocking... wait... <name type="person">Jay</name>?</s>
        <s>Stay calm, stay calm.</s>
        <s>It's been... Gosh, so long!</s>
        <s>How is he here?</s>
        <s>Did <name type="person">Nick</name> know him all along?</s>
        <s>Stay neutral, <name type="person">Daisy</name>.</s>
        <s>Is he still angry that I married <name type="person">Tom</name>?</s>
        <s>I didn't wait for him.</s>
        <s>Does he have a lover now?</s>
        <s>Where's <name type="person">Nick</name> going?</s>
        <s>I feel nervous.</s>
        <s>I'm scared.</s>
        <s>He... he remembers the exact month when we last met.</s>
        <s>He must have been waiting, then.</s>
        <s>I want to ask so many questions... how did he fare?</s>
        <s>He seems rich now.</s>
        <s>Is it... too late?</s>
        <s>I have never really been loved by <name type="person">Tom</name>, so why not just... but how could <name type="person">Jay</name> ever forgive me?</s>
        <s>Is it too outrageous to be with him again?</s>
      </p>
